question: Which botanical garden can be found in Kota Bogor, Indonesia?
asked_question_translated: Hvilken botanisk hage finner du i Kota Bogor, Indonesia?
answer: I Kota Bogor, Indonesia finner du Kebun Raya Bogor (Bogor Botaniske Hage).
answer_translated_eng: I Bogor City, Indonesia finner du Bogor Botanical Garden (Bogor Botaniske Hage).
